name: Iman Europe - All On Time
metadata:
{"name": "All On Time 1/100", "description": "if you would've told me a year ago that i'd be where i am today, i promise i wouldn't believe you. i'm writing this from my hotel room in new orleans, preparing for my presentation at ESSENCE Fest on Saturday, July 2, 2022. not only am i being honored for my music, but for my knowledge and work in Web3 as well. it feels good to be seen. it feels good to watch all things come together on time for me. finally.

to celebrate and commemorate this huge moment for me at ESSENCE Fest, i can't think of any song better than "All On Time" to mint. this song is about perseverance in the midst of uncertainty, and i believe that that is the very mindset that got me where i am today.

this NFT is being placed in an ESSENCE Fest gallery yo!! like what!!? idk about you, but i think that's pretty f*cking cool. shout out to ESSENCE for seeing the vision and shining light on music NFTs so that our community can understand this space better. and shoutout to anyone who resonates with this song deep enough to collect it.

may these lyrics remind you that things are working in your favor even when you don't see it.
may you never forget that itb�s all on time.

with love,
iman europe
